text: Fritz William Michel (born 1980)Premier Ministre par intérim: Jean-Michel Lapin depuis le 21/03/2019 Appartenance politique: indépendant election- politique.com was nominated for Prime Minister of Haiti on 22 July 2019, but wasn't confirmed by parliament. He was previously the Chief Accountant at the Ministry of the Economy and Finance from 2009 to 2011. ==References== Category:21st-century Haitian politicians Category:Living people Category:1980 births
title: Fritz William Michel
